# ELITE UX INVARIANTS

> **The GettUpp Luxury Standard**

## 1. Fluid Motion
All interactions (hover, entrance, scroll) MUST use Framer Motion with custom spring/inertia.
Required spring config: stiffness: 100, damping: 20
No linear animations allowed.

## 2. Reduced Motion
All 3D and Framer Motion effects MUST respect prefers-reduced-motion.

## 3. Glass Fidelity
Glassmorphic cards must have:
- backdrop-blur: 20px
- border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)

## 4. 3D Performance
All Three.js/R3F sections MUST have:
- Static image fallback for mobile
- Explicit loading state (Skeleton/Progress Bar)
- Performance monitoring

## 5. Typography Authority
Large headings (900 weight) must utilize:
- Metallic gradients
- Glow effects
- Brand-aligned styling

## 6. No Flat State
Every interactive element (Button, Card, Link) must have visual elevation or glow feedback on hover.

## 7. No Layout Shift
All dynamic sections must have:
- Predefined aspect ratios
- Skeleton placeholders
- Reserved space for async content
